{"type":"message","id":"4dfe1c47","parentId":"9c02e8f3","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:41:45.553Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The build succeeded. Let me summarize what was accomplished.","thinkingSignature":"cbce66ad41c85367e2ddf3b28d9e522f2425dabc0e3cfb7d79cbf0eb23c241e1"},{"type":"text","text":"Build succeeded. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## What Was Built\n\n### `src/lib/gateway.ts`\n- **`sendChatMessage(agentId, message, sessionKey)`** — Posts to `/tools/invoke` with the `sessions_send` tool, sends Bobby's message to Dean's session key, and returns Dean's response text\n- **`getChatHistory(agentId)`** — Queries `sessions_list` for the agent's session, reads the `transcriptPath` JSONL file if available, parses it into `ChatMessage[]`\n- Added proper `Authorization: Bearer` header to all gateway calls\n\n### `src/components/MessageModal.tsx`\n- **Dean only:** Full real-time chat interface:\n  - Scrollable message history with auto-scroll to bottom on new messages\n  - User messages → indigo/violet gradient bubbles, right-aligned, white text\n  - Dean messages → frosted glass (`bg-white/[0.07]`) bubbles, left-aligned, 🤖 prefix\n  - Timestamps on every message (subtle, small text)\n  - Typing indicator (3 bouncing dots) while waiting for Dean to respond\n  - Enter or ⌘+Enter to send, Escape to close\n  - Clean frosted glass input bar at bottom with gradient send button\n- **All other agents (Emmy, X, Finn, YoYo, Rex, DJ, Cody):** Show a friendly \"Chat coming soon for [Agent]\" modal instead of the chat UI\n\n### `src/App.tsx`\n- Removed the old `onSend` prop from `MessageModal` — the modal now handles its own send logic internally via `sendChatMessage`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":12207,"output":364,"cacheRead":16299,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28870,"cost":{"input":0.0036620999999999997,"output":0.0004368,"cacheRead":0.000977939999999999