{"type":"message","id":"dbbd55af","parentId":"4dfe1c47","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:41:45.800Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-23 20:40 EDT] Bobby also wants: add a beautiful animated gradient background to the app so the frosted glass effect is very visible. Use deep purple (#1a0a2e), indigo (#0f0f3d), and subtle teal (#0a1a1f) gradients. Make it layered and animated (slow color shifts). The glass cards need to POP against this background — right now the black background makes the glass barely noticeable. Think Apple Vision Pro backgrounds — dark but colorful, with luminous orbs floating behind the glass panels."}],"timestamp":1774312905798,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:cody:telegram:direct:8212808444","sourceChannel":"telegram","sourceTool":"sessions_send"}}}
