{"type":"message","id":"8db6c494","parentId":"d4ee116a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:42:54.207Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to make sure the glass cards pop more. The current glass cards use `bg-white/[0.06]` which on a black background is subtle. With the new colorful background, they should look much better. But I might need to increase the glass opacity slightly to ensure the frosted glass effect is visible.\n\nLet me also check the AgentGrid and Header components to see how the glass cards are styled.","thinkingSignature":"56c9f4e20bb87ca117d75b118f293f43852859e09dba1795f8c5a09da377b6c2"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me also check the glass card styles in the AgentGrid and Header:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_at6phoa86bch_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/src/components/AgentGrid.tsx"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_at6phoa86bch_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/src/components/Header.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15985,"output":177,"cacheRead":14864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31026,"cost":{"input":0.004795499999999999,"output":0.00021239999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00089184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005899739999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774312968552,"responseId":"06111108434d6c6039bf2501f9a05511"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fbfadcee","parentId":"8db6c494","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:42:54.227Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_at6phoa86bch_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import type { Agent, AgentState } from '../types';\nimport { AGENTS } from '../types';\nimport { AgentCard } from './AgentCard';\nimport { SkeletonCard } from './SkeletonCard';\n\ninterface AgentGridProps {\n  agentStates: Record<string, AgentState>;\n  initialized: boolean;\n  onAgentClick: (agent: Agent) => void;\n}\n\nexport const AgentGrid = ({ agentStates, initialized, onAgentClick }: AgentGridProps) => {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5\">\n      {AGENTS.map((agent) => {\n        if (!initialized) {\n          return <SkeletonCard key={agent.id} />;\n        }\n        return (\n          <AgentCard\n            key={agent.id}\n            agent={agent}\n            state={agentStates[agent.id] ?? { status: 'offline', lastActive: null, session: null }}\n            onClick={onAgentClick}\n          />\n        );\n      })}\n    </div>\n  );\n};\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774312974222}}
{"type":"message","id":"01b06e21","parentId":"fbfadcee","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:42:54.232Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_at6phoa86bch_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import type { ConnectionState } from '../types';\nimport { useEffect, useState } from 'react';\n\ninterface HeaderProps {\n  connectionState: ConnectionState;\n}\n\nfunction useLiveClock() {\n  const [time, setTime] = useState(() => new Date());\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const id = setInterval(() => setTime(new Date()), 1000);\n    return () => clearInterval(id);\n  }, []);\n  return time;\n}\n\nconst CONNECTION_CONFIG = {\n  connected: {\n    dotClass: 'bg-status-online shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(52,211,153,0.8)]',\n    label: 'Connected',\n  },\n  polling: {\n    dotClass: 'bg-yellow-400 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(250,204,21,0.8)] animate-pulse',\n    label: 'Polling...',\n  },\n  disconnected: {\n    dotClass: 'bg-status-error shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(248,113,113,0.8)]',\n    label: 'Disconnected',\n  },\n};\n\nexport const Header = ({ connectionState }: HeaderProps) => {\n  const time = useLiveClock();\n  const config = CONNECTION_CONFIG[connectionState];\n\n  const pad = (n: number) => n.toString().padStart(2, '0');\n  const timeStr = `${pad(time.getHours())}:${pad(time.getMinutes())}:${pad(time.getSeconds())}`;\n\n  return (\n    <header className=\"flex items-center justify-between px-2 pb-6\">\n      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n        <h1 className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-100 tracking-tight\">Mission Control</h1>\n        <div className={`w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full ${config.dotClass}`} />\n        <span className=\"text-xs text-slate-500 hidden sm:inline\">{config.label}</span>\n      </div>\n      <time\n        dateTime={time.toISOString()}\n        className=\"font-mono text-xl font-medium text-slate-300 tabular-nums\"\n      >\n        {timeStr}\n      </time>\n    </header>\n  );\n};\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774312974227}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6310bcd","parentId":"01b06e21","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:42:56.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me look at the AgentCard to see the glass styling:","thinkingSignature":"c634bbf7e212e8e98e738d50c009183952adde2e7e41876f53658651f608eca7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7z2h8ufyv4hf_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/src/components/AgentCard.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":16885,"output":57,"cacheRead":14864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31806,"cost":{"input":0.0050655,"output":0.0000684,"cacheRead":0.00089184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006025739999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774312974232,"responseId":"0611110ed6b4ea7f94a458a38784d9fd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a71f01e","parentId":"e6310bcd","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:42:56.597Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7z2h8ufyv4hf_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import type { Agent, AgentState } from '../types';\nimport { StatusBadge } from './StatusBadge';\n\ninterface AgentCardProps {\n  agent: Agent;\n  state: AgentState;\n  onClick: (agent: Agent) => void;\n}\n\nfunction formatRelativeTime(timestamp: number | null): string {\n  if (!timestamp) return 'Never';\n  const diff = Date.now() - timestamp;\n  if (diff < 60_000) return 'Just now';\n  if (diff < 3_600_000) return `${Math.floor(diff / 60_000)}m ago`;\n  if (diff < 86_400_000) return `${Math.floor(diff / 3_600_000)}h ago`;\n  return `${Math.floor(diff / 86_400_000)}d ago`;\n}\n\nexport const AgentCard = ({ agent, state, onClick }: AgentCardProps) => {\n  return (\n    <button\n      onClick={() => onClick(agent)}\n      className=\"\n        group relative w-full backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6\n        flex flex-col items-center gap-3 text-left\n        transition-all duration-200 ease-out\n        hover:bg-white/[0.08] hover:border-white/20 hover:scale-[1.02]\n        active:scale-[0.99]\n        focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent-indigo/50\n      \"\n      style={{ boxShadow: '0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)' }}\n    >\n      {/* Ambient glow for online/busy */}\n      {state.status === 'online' && (\n        <div className=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl bg-status-online/5 pointer-events-none\" />\n      )}\n      {state.status === 'busy' && (\n        <div className=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl bg-status-busy/5 pointer-events-none animate-pulse\" />\n      )}\n\n      {/* Emoji avatar */}\n      <div className=\"text-5xl select-none\">{agent.emoji}</div>\n\n      {/* Agent name */}\n      <div className=\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100 text-center leading-tight\">{agent.name}</div>\n\n      {/* Role */}\n      <div className=\"text-xs text-slate-400 text-center leading-snug\">{agent.role}</div>\n\n      {/* Status badge */}\n      <div className=\"mt-1\">\n        <StatusBadge status={state.status} />\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Last active */}\n      <div className=\"text-xs text-slate-500 font-mono\">\n        {formatRelativeTime(state.lastActive)}\n      </div>\n    </button>\n  );\n};\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774312976590}}
{"type":"message","id":"209a4023","parentId":"7a71f01e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:43:09.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The AgentCard uses `bg-white/5` which on a black background is barely visible. Now that we have the colorful background, these cards should actually pop more. But to make them even more visible, I could:\n\n1. Slightly increase the opacity of the glass\n2. Add a more prominent glow/shadow that catches the background colors\n\nLet me boost the glass effect slightly so it really pops against the colorful background. I'll change `bg-white/5` to `bg-white/8` and add a subtle colored shadow.\n\nActually, let me also add a colored glow to the cards that picks up the background colors. Something like a subtle indigo glow at the bottom.\n\n\nI should refine the AgentCard styling to use slightly more opaque glass—bumping `bg-white/5` up to `bg-white/[0.08]` and enhancing the shadow with a colored glow effect that complements the background.","thinkingSignature":"a78c3fe315c008917460924789b22c7e0ae8c7c6575c5df96cc21b8bc01cdda5"},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me boost the glass card opacity so they really pop against the colorful background:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t27fb37hc02q_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/src/components/AgentCard.tsx","old_string":"      className=\"\n        group relative w-full backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6\n        flex flex-col items-center gap-3 text-left\n        transition-all duration-200 ease-out\n        hover:bg-white/[0.08] hover:border-white/20 hover:scale-[1.02]\n        active:scale-[0.99]\n        focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent-indigo/50\n      \"\n      style={{ boxShadow: '0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)' }}\n    >","new_string":"      className=\"\n        group relative w-full backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/[0.08] border border-white/[0.12] rounded-2xl p-6\n        flex flex-col items-center gap-3 text-left\n        transition-all duration-200 ease-out\n        hover:bg-white/[0.11] hover:border-white/[0.22] hover:scale-[1.02]\n        active:scale-[0.99]\n        focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent-indigo/50\n      \"\n      style={{\n        boxShadow:\n          '0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), 0 0 60px rgba(88,28,135,0.08), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.08)',\n      }}\n    >"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":17539,"output":583,"cacheRead":14864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32986,"cost":{"input":0.005261699999999999,"output":0.0006996,"cacheRead":0.00089184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006853139999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774312976598,"responseId":"061111105c0c85556b52c5ece977fc04"}}
