{"type":"message","id":"da4f9acf","parentId":"c5358707","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:44:22.808Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Build succeeded. Let me give a brief summary of what was done.","thinkingSignature":"b11cf8f9fe3318c599021aae074e043d684be9c6f3ec29e8fafd3aaeb1e1a569"},{"type":"text","text":"Build succeeded. Here's what was added:\n\n## Apple Vision Pro Animated Background\n\n**New `Background.tsx` component** — 6 layered luminous orbs floating behind the UI:\n\n| Orb | Color | Position | Animation |\n|-----|-------|----------|-----------|\n| 1 | Purple (#582c87 → #2d0a4e) | Top-left, massive | 22s drift + 8s pulse |\n| 2 | Indigo (#1e1e64) | Center-right | 28s drift |\n| 3 | Teal (#0a3c3c → #0a1a1f) | Bottom-center | 25s drift |\n| 4 | Violet (#6d28d9) | Top-right | 19s drift + hue shift |\n| 5 | Deep magenta | Bottom-right | 32s drift + color shift |\n| 6 | Bright indigo glow | Center-left | 16s drift |\n\nPlus: noise texture overlay + edge vignette for depth.\n\n**Glass card upgrades:**\n- `AgentCard`: `bg-white/5` → `bg-white/[0.08]`, added purple glow shadow + brighter borders\n- `MessageModal`: Both chat and \"coming soon\" modals bumped to `bg-white/[0.10]`\n- Chat bubbles: dean messages → `bg-white/[0.09]` with slightly lighter borders\n- Status glows: now use radial gradient underneath each card (green for online, purple for busy) so they cast colored light onto the background orbs\n\nAll orbs animate with completely independent timing (16s–32s periods, staggered delays) so the motion feels organic and never synchronized."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":21713,"output":364,"cacheRead":14864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36941,"cost":{"input":0.0065138999999999996,"output":0.0004368,"cacheRead":0.00089184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00784254}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774313052172,"responseId":"0611115c0c67cb69999ecdf7bc726136"}}
